local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["fatality"]={"fatality","[fə'tælɪtɪ; feɪ-]","[fə'tæləti]","n.(事故或战争等造成的)死亡",'n.(事故或战争等造成的)死亡,灾祸,天命，致命性','There have been ten swimming ||fatalities|| (ie Ten people have lost their lives while swimming) this summer.','今年夏季已有十人游泳遇溺.','There was a strange fatality about their both losing their jobs on the same day.','他们两人同一天失去工作, 真是天意叵测.'}
